1.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>작성 규칙</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">- 완성에 목적을 두지 않고, 지식 축적에 목적을 둘 것\n- 용어들의 뜻을 최대한 간략하게 정리하여 작성할 것\n- 추가 내용은 별도의 글로 작성하여 링크 추가할 것\n- 영어로 번역해도 의미가 변질되지 않도록 작성할 것</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">자음 순서 : ㄱ ㄲ ㄴ ㄷ ㄸ ㄹ ㅁ ㅂ ㅃ ㅅ ㅆ ㅇ ㅈ ㅉ ㅊ ㅋ ㅌ ㅍ ㅎ\n모음 순서 : ㅏ ㅐ ㅑ ㅒ ㅓ ㅔ ㅕ ㅖ ㅗ ㅘ ㅙ ㅚ ㅛ ㅜ ㅝ ㅞ ㅟ ㅠ ㅡ ㅢ ㅣ\n받침 순서 : ㄱ ㄲ ㄳ ㄴ ㄵ ㄶ ㄷ ㄹ ㄺ ㄻ ㄼ ㄽ ㄾ ㄿ ㅀ ㅁ ㅂ ㅄ ㅅ ㅆ ㅇ ㅈ ㅊ ㅋ ㅌ ㅍ ㅎ</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"ㄱ\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E3%84%B1\" aria-label=\"ㄱ permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ㄱ</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>골벵이표(<code class=\"language-text\">@</code>, At Sign, 앳)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"ㄴ\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E3%84%B4\" aria-label=\"ㄴ permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ㄴ</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>논리 회로(Logic Gate)</li>\n<li>느낌표(<code class=\"language-text\">!</code>, Exclamation Mark) : 일반적으로 뱅(Bang), 스크리머(Screamer) 등으로 불림</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"ㄷ\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E3%84%B7\" aria-label=\"ㄷ permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ㄷ</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>따옴표(<code class=\"language-text\">'</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">\"</code>, Quotation Mark, Quotes) : 인용부, 인용 부호라고도 함</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"ㄹ\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E3%84%B9\" aria-label=\"ㄹ permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ㄹ</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>리처드 브레이스웨이트(Richard Braithwait)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"ㅁ\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E3%85%81\" aria-label=\"ㅁ permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ㅁ</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>물결표(<code class=\"language-text\">~</code>, Tilde, 틸다) : 홈 디렉토리(Unix 계열 OS), 부정(NOT) 연산자(C 언어) 를 나타냄</li>\n<li>물음표(<code class=\"language-text\">?</code>, Question Mark)</li>\n<li>밑줄 문자(<code class=\"language-text\">_</code>, Underscore, 언더스코어) : ‘Underbar’ 라고도 부름, 공백 문자 대신 사용되기도 함</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"ㅂ\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E3%85%82\" aria-label=\"ㅂ permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ㅂ</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>바이트(Byte)</li>\n<li>백분율 기호(<code class=\"language-text\">%</code>, Percent Sign)</li>\n<li>별표(<code class=\"language-text\">*</code>, Asterisk, 애스터리스크) : ‘Star’ 라고 발음함(전산학, 수학)</li>\n<li>붙임표(<code class=\"language-text\">-</code>, Hyphen, 하이픈)</li>\n<li>비트(Bit)</li>\n<li>빗금(<code class=\"language-text\">/</code>, Slash, 슬래시) : ‘Solidus’ 라고도 부름(유니코드)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"ㅅ\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E3%85%85\" aria-label=\"ㅅ permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ㅅ</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>삿갓표(<code class=\"language-text\">^</code>, Caret, 캐럿) : 비트 XOR 또는 지수 연산자로 사용됨(일부 프로그래밍 언어)</li>\n<li>소프트웨어(Software)</li>\n<li>수직선 기호(<code class=\"language-text\">|</code>, Pipe, 파이프) : ‘Bar’, ‘Stick’ 이라고도 부름, 논리합(OR) 연산자로 사용됨</li>\n<li>쉼표(<code class=\"language-text\">,</code>, Comma, 콤마)</li>\n<li>스네이크 케이스(Snake Case) : <code class=\"language-text\">this_is_snake_case</code></li>\n<li>쌍점(<code class=\"language-text\">:</code>, Colon, 콜론)</li>\n<li>쌍반점(<code class=\"language-text\">;</code>, Semicolon, 세미콜론)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"ㅇ\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E3%85%87\" aria-label=\"ㅇ permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ㅇ</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>앰퍼샌드(<code class=\"language-text\">&amp;</code>, Ampersand) : 논리곱(AND) 연산자로 사용됨</li>\n<li>역슬래시(<code class=\"language-text\">\\</code>, Backslash, 백슬래시) : ‘Escape’ 라고 부름(C 언어, Unix)</li>\n<li>우물정자(<code class=\"language-text\">#</code>, Hash, 해시) : ‘번호 기호’, ‘샵’, ‘Number Sign’, ‘Pound Sign’ 이라고도 부름</li>\n<li>운영체제(Operating System, OS)</li>\n<li>의사결정(Decision Making)</li>\n<li>인터넷(Internet)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"ㅈ\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E3%85%88\" aria-label=\"ㅈ permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ㅈ</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>중앙 처리 장치(Central Processing Unit, CPU)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"ㅊ\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E3%85%8A\" aria-label=\"ㅊ permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ㅊ</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>찰스 배비지(Charles Babbage)</li>\n<li>추상화(Abstraction)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"ㅋ\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E3%85%8B\" aria-label=\"ㅋ permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ㅋ</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>카멜 케이스(Camel Case) : <code class=\"language-text\">thisIsCamelCase</code></li>\n<li>컴포넌트(Component) : 구성 요소</li>\n<li>컴퓨터(Computer)</li>\n<li>컴퓨팅(Computing)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"ㅌ\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E3%85%8C\" aria-label